metadata.name: Rise Of The Dark King
metadata.description:
In a period of my life, the sun of dark king rose and he reigned over my inner world !

During this time, I experienced a lot of suffering and sadness ,but after a while he planted some seeds inside me ; Seeds of hope and creativity !
He taught me how to take care of them and always be strong...
